<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Important Update from Golden Field</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f5f7;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 26px;
            color: #222;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .message {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-left: 4px solid #007BFF;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #333;
            white-space: pre-wrap; /* Ensures that line breaks and spaces are preserved */
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            background-color: #007BFF;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }

        .footer {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #888;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #007BFF;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Important Update from Golden Field</h2>
        <p>We hope this message finds you well. We are reaching out to provide you with an important update. Please read the details below:</p>

        <div class="message">
            <p><%= message %></p>
        </div>

        <p>If you have any questions or need more information, please feel free to contact us at any time.</p>

        <a href="mailto:moruditech@gmail.com" class="cta-button">Contact Us</a>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you for your time, and we look forward to connecting with you.</p>
            <p>Best regards,</p>
            <p>The Golden Field Team</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
